        "title": "Isaiah Tells of \"Last Days\"",
        "introduction": "Perhaps it is during this time of jubilant rededication that Isaiah shares with excitement the visions he has received about the coming of the Messiah and the ultimate triumph of good over evil. Using vivid and powerful imagery, Isaiah describes the time when the wicked will be punished and the righteous blessed forever."
